snippet.title: The EdCo Incident | New Indie Horror Game | Final Trailer #3
snippet.description:
Feel free to Like and Subscribe!

Download the completed game here!
http://www.mediafire.com/file/7cp19n3kbkdckl4/The_EdCo_Incident.zip/file

This PowerPoint game almost two years in the making is finally done

For those who won't be able to download the game, subscribe to ArthurPlays to see his upcoming video on it: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCq2mmZCVlQ4nPSGj3E6oi3g

Previous EdCo Incident trailers:

First Trailer: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XGjoAxKnFJs

Second Trailer: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2-ImXU-tAkk
